          <h2>Intelligentely&trade; organize your life</h2>
          <p>By carefully combining information from many sources we will help you organize your photos based on location, calendars, tagged people, photo analyzing and face recognition.</p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
