        <img class="featurette-image pull-right" src="../assets/img/examples/browser-icon-safari.png">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Frankly. All your photos <span class="muted">are not fantastic.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">We promise to help you to automatically hide those duplicates, under exposed, over exposed pictures and snaps of whiteboard tables. We use information such as viewing time, clicks, shares, time and date as clues</p>
